ADDITIONAL TERMS FOR PSV-OPAQUE PROJECT:

This project contains theoretical designs and simulations for advanced aerospace 
systems. The PSV-OPAQUE fighter aircraft design is a conceptual research project 
and does not represent any actual military hardware or classified information.

All technical specifications, performance characteristics, and system capabilities 
described in this project are theoretical, educational, or based on publicly 
available information. This software is intended solely for:

- Academic research and education
- Aerospace engineering studies  
- Software development learning
- Theoretical system modeling
- Open source collaboration

Users are responsible for ensuring compliance with all applicable laws, 
regulations, and export controls in their jurisdiction when using this software.

The author disclaims any responsibility for the use of this software in actual 
military applications, weapons development, or any activities that may violate 
international law or regulations.